{"tid":168952,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"即使面對屬性剋制,公廁蝠宜依舊能奇蹟獲勝","createTime":"2017-03-24T01:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T09:03:46.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9291c4f6dc2b5212adc80d7cc1602c0a1bfae1","tid":168952,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/17504304_1486311618047119_8096070282442788249_o.jpg?oh=13c6fbaf4f6c6f5ed3dbd25e7cd8dcf7&amp;oe=59727802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F17504304_1486311618047119_8096070282442788249_o.jpg%3Foh%3D13c6fbaf4f6c6f5ed3dbd25e7cd8dcf7%26oe%3D59727802&h=aff8ad25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開台打緊白金版,宜家就開始準備黑版存檔,行山洞同樣遇到成車公廁蝠,不過今次公廁蝠個樣咁cute,所以就唔忍心捉左佢,但佢係超能力屬性會被蟲剋但打蟲道館時唔記得補血得翻公廁蝠用,諗住蟲剋超死梗,點知有愛有希望,隻公廁蝠竟然出動那種招式將對手一擊必殺,友情是魔法!"},{"pid":"78486c04fae24ed70b18baf612c200f1ee99b3b3","tid":168952,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9d8a6c919d10acbccc7ae456098c5efd15c617","tid":168952,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e620e52c31393ae5cad0098fc4dce451bf6422d","tid":168952,"uid":56320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"d618dee22268af32587c90724a61dd86fb14d763","tid":168952,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e68245e7a3ecca3d06f337731b09e08eac63ad0","tid":168952,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re